The abandoned Sealed Route has been compromised by Synod occupation forces using the old quarantine corridors to move relic-hazard material past active Reach inspection networks, directly violating Violet Compact transit documentation standards. Whisper Cell commandant leadership, quarantine breach horrors released as tactical cover, and tunnel sentries controlling access must all be eliminated before the Sealed Route can be re-secured. The Midgaard postmaster requires elimination of one of each to break the occupation.
The Synod occupation of the Sealed Route has been dismantled. Quarantine breach horrors have been neutralized, the tunnel sentry network is cleared, and the Whisper Cell commandant directorate has been eliminated. The postmaster has forwarded the relic-hazard incident report through the Violet Compact for cross-referencing with the Khar'Daan funerary authority.
